events.name: WordPress Singapore Meetup Feb 2016
events.description:
Hello all. Hope everyone had a great Chinese New Year!

Our February meetup is focused on Content Generation and SEO.

We have a blogger, one of the rare few that writes well who will talk about her experiences with lifestyle blogging - 沈诗敏 (Carrie Sim)

We also have an SEO geek who's gonna show you how easy it is to achieve great Search Engine Optimisation via using Yoast SEO for WordPress - Tommy Koh 

It will be held at Amazon Web Services so please sign up!

Light snacks & beer provided courtesy of AWS!

http://www.meetup.com/WordPress-Singapore/events/228481078/

events.name: 2月の飲み会
events.description: シンガポール日本人エンジニア会、２月の飲み会を開催します。 私主催者の近澤は３月でシンガポールを離れるため、これがひとまず最後の参加となります。エンジニア会の運営は他の方に引き継ぎますので、これからも飲み会は継続します！ 場所はいつもの川味人家になりました！
events.location: 川味人家 (Chuan Wei Ren Jia), 17 Mosque Street Singapore 059497 6220 5766

events.name: talk.js
events.description: The nex talk.js will be on Monday 22nd February. Scheduled Talks • JavaScript News - Tim Oxley (@timoxley)  • JS1k - Joshua Koo (@zz85)  • Meteor JS + Interactive dance performance - Calvin Tan (@calvintan) • loopback.io Framework: Models, Phases and Identities - Stephan Wissel (@stwissel) Location PayPal Singapore Suntec Tower 5 5 Temasek Boulevard #09-01 Singapore Venue, free drinks and pizza sponsored by PayPal. Remember to bring photo ID to get through building security. Feel free to ask questions in the SingaporeJS gitter room: https://gitter.im/SingaporeJS/discussions See you there!
events.location: PayPal Singapore, Suntec Tower 5, 5 Temasek Boulevard #09-01
